game.name: Ladybug Pregnant Caring
game.description:
Your luck is on high today as you will get a chance to spend time with your favorite Ladybug in our brand new doctor game. Join Ladybug Pregnant Caring and get a pleasure of providing the needful assistance with a lovely woman when nobody is there to assist her! You are her last hope, so make sure that she will get the treatment on time during her pregnancy. Avoid wasting your time as her pain starts increasing with the time! 

This beautiful princess is enjoying the best phase of her life i.e. pregnancy, but a sudden pain has encouraged her to rush to the hospital. Take her to the nearest healthcare facility and help her get the complete treatment she needs at this time in this one of the best games for girls! She looks pretty nervous. Your objective is to check the present condition of her health with the medical tools you see at the bottom of the screen. Check her temperature, blood pressure, heartbeat and give her a pain analgesic!

Her current health condition would help let you know that if she is now ready to deliver a baby safely. After the delivery of her baby, you also have to analyze the health of her baby. Being her personal physician, you should do all the things to keep her feel relax. Do not forget to help the ladybug to have the needful vitamins and healthy food. Make sure to examine the health of the princess and her baby perfectly in this html5 caring game. Atmegame.com offers thousands of free doctor games to play online without download.
